{"tid":2233320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣樓上舖慘蝕3,200萬  「物流張」見紅 6年貶值44%","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:29:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b0421c1244a9b7c741e3c0f613ef987511ec58ab","tid":2233320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/ODMLPH3AIBCE5N2DMWF2KOHMDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FODMLPH3AIBCE5N2DMWF2KOHMDI%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=6f8696c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2FODMLPH3AIBCE5N2DMWF2KOHMDI%2F&h=6e12189a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201007/ODMLPH3AIBCE5N2DMWF2KOHMDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣樓上舖慘蝕3,200萬 <br />\n「物流張」見紅 6年貶值44%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jxQpqbObJDYRzMx9SwSD7jPqawU=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RRLZVHQTU5DJHHHLVE4PQNY6MU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjxQpqbObJDYRzMx9SwSD7jPqawU%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRRLZVHQTU5DJHHHLVE4PQNY6MU.jpg&h=f90e7bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■銅鑼灣銀座式商廈Oliv剛錄全層易手，賣出價4,000萬元，勁蝕44%。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港「封關」逾半年，訪港旅客人數大跌近99%，零售市況淡靜，核心區地舖價格回落，手持「樓上舖」同樣要損手離場。銅鑼灣銀座式商廈Oliv全層，原由有「物流張」之稱的資深投資者張順宜持有，惟最新則勁蝕約3,152萬元或44%轉手離場，料屬區內同類物業最大額蝕讓成交。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：區內零售舖吹冷風 空置率13%新高<br />\n<br />\n零售市道疲弱，不少租戶相繼棄租核心區舖位，其中銅鑼灣區過往以遊客生意作重心，該區近月商舖空置率升至雙位數水平，創歷史新高，連帶區內相關價格亦持續受壓，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「物流張」頻見血價沽貨<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，上述樓層由佰立有限公司於2014年1月，以約7,152萬元購入；按公司註冊處文件，公司秘書登記為資深投資者張順宜，而公司董事則為張順吉。換言之，張順宜或相關人士是次沽出Oliv樓層，賬面蝕約3,152萬元，物業6年間貶值約44%，料創下區內最大額樓上舖蝕讓個案。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，「物流張」近期亦陸續蝕放手上物業。市場消息指，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，荃灣大河道77至89號寶成地下9號舖，面積約900方呎，於上月以2,600萬元易手。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Sharp早前蝕2,688萬<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，本港銀座式商廈近年不乏蝕讓個案。其中毗鄰上述Oliv、位於霎東街11至13號The Sharp低層全層，面積約1,580方呎，早於7月以約3,000萬元沽出，呎價僅18,987元，屬該廈新低成交。原業主於2013年以5,688萬元購入，持貨7年，賬面蝕2,688萬元離場，蝕幅高達47%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wTDPifazetcpYB58xU1ZxKaf0UI=/747x670/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJ5XYGJSFNALROUSPCKXMNXLGI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwTDPifazetcpYB58xU1ZxKaf0UI%3D%2F747x670%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJ5XYGJSFNALROUSPCKXMNXLGI.gif&h=becf6f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ca1f7e6c1a5d17deb0c5c442eca0afcf1dcac47","tid":2233320,"uid":8308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:53:53.000Z","msg":"商舖拎黎炒仲好意思報出黎"},{"pid":"6bbdb78b9c543e26a4cda957b38c2cf6dbf0036f","tid":2233320,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"屌, 大把錢驚閪咩, strong hold嘛"},{"pid":"238e5e0eeb3fea0eca136c83cc7c6abf51bc7b89","tid":2233320,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"話時話, 蘋果新聞唔係應該只share一少段咩?"},{"pid":"1439482c39ffce5e0a1a205ad327944803b05c90","tid":2233320,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"要搬錢走蝕住賣都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd236140d4c94fa0d0798ee791f536717d93fbc6","tid":2233320,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"限晒聚都<br />\n又爆第4波源頭不明<br />\n<br />\n大家都知咩事<br />\n繼續開支那關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d19c3948dd2179e6290c7731fc68661e5649f94","tid":2233320,"uid":123020,"